data.name: ReadCsePerson
data.value: select top(1) NUMB from CKT_CSE_PERSON where NUMB = @numb

data.name: ReadCsePersonAddress
data.value: select top(1) IDENTIFIER, CSP_NUMBER, ZDEL_START_DATE, SEND_DATE, SOURCE, STREET_1, STREET_2, CITY, TYPE, WORKER_ID, VERIFIED_DATE, END_DATE, END_CODE, ZDEL_VERIFIED_CODE, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, LAST_UPDATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, CREATED_BY, [STATE], ZIP_CODE, ZIP4, ZIP3, STREET_3, STREET_4, PROVINCE, POSTAL_CODE, COUNTRY, LOCATION_TYPE, COUNTY from CKT_CSE_PERS_ADDR where (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER) and (TYPE = @type) and (LOCATION_TYPE = @locationType) and (STREET_1 = @street1) and (CITY = @city) and ([STATE] = @state)
